==English==

{{wikipedia|Kingdom of God}}

===Etymology===
A calque of {{etyl|grc}} {{l|grc|Βασιλεία τῶν Οὐρανῶν}} (Basileia tōn Ouranōn), from the [[w:Gospel of Matthew|Gospel of Matthew]].

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun|sg=[[kingdom|Kingdom]] of [[heaven|Heaven]]}}

# {{Christianity}} A concept of heaven as a [[hierarchical]] [[dominion]] with [[God]] at the top and a [[court]] of [[saint]]s, [[archangel]]s and [[angel]]s.
# The place where God rules and reigns.

